Enforces that every member crate in the workspace opts into the workspace lint table by declaring `[lints] workspace = true` in its Cargo.toml. Silent non-compliance silently disables all workspace lint enforcement for the affected crate, so this check fails CI to surface the omission early.

Uses `git ls-files` to enumerate all Cargo.toml files (including nested ones) to avoid racing concurrent `target/` writes. Skips the virtual workspace root and any file that lacks a `[package]` table. For each member crate, runs an awk state machine that verifies a `workspace = true` line appears inside the `[lints]` table specifically, not in `[workspace]` or elsewhere; the state machine resets on any new table header.